## Loomio
++
Features:
	- workflow:
		- Start a group to collaborate with people on Loomio
		- Invite people into your group+
		- Start a discussion on any topic
		- Make a proposal to see how everyone feels about a particular course of action
		- Decide together - anyone can agree, abstain, disagree, or block â€“ so you can see how 	everyone feels about the proposal.
	- threads dashboard show all suggestions with their status
	- you can post comments on a discussion
	- FOSS (github), and SaaS (~20$/month per group, or 179$/month with unlimited groups)
	- possibility for sub-groups

